title._content: NSW servicemen portraits, 1918-19 - Richard Paul Lindsell

description._content: Richard Lindsell enlisted in Sydney on May 25,1918. He gave his date of birth as April 10 1899. It was discovered, however, that he was actually born in 1900 and a note to this effect and a letter of permission to enlist from his mother is included in his service file. Pte 65777 3rd Battalion RTA 23.7.1919 Format: Photograph Find more detailed information about this photograph: acms.sl.nsw.gov.au/item/itemDetailPaged.aspx?itemID=431784 From the collection of the State Library of New South Wales www.sl.nsw.gov.au
